@deffn {Scheme Procedure} avahi-service [#:avahi @var{avahi}] @
          [#:host-name #f] [#:publish? #t] [#:ipv4? #t] @ [#:ipv6? #t] [#:wide-area?
#f] @ [#:domains-to-browse '()] [#:debug? #f] Return a service that runs
